#: src/Form/SettingsFieldset.php:30
msgid ""
"Specify how images are displayed on item and media pages. \"Large\" shows "
"the standard Omeka large thumbnail. \"Tile\" renders images in a zoomable "
"OpenSeadragon viewer using pre-tiled data when available. \"Original\" "
"serves the original file (not recommended for large images). This is "
"independent of IIIF viewers (Universal Viewer, Mirador, Diva…)."
msgstr ""

#: src/Form/SettingsFieldset.php:32
msgid "Large thumbnail (default)"
msgstr "Vignette large (défaut)"

#: src/Form/SettingsFieldset.php:33
msgid "Zoomable viewer (OpenSeadragon with tiles)"
msgstr "Visionneuse zoomable (OpenSeadragon avec tuiles)"

#: src/Form/SettingsFieldset.php:34
msgid "Original file (not recommended for images larger than 1-10 MB)"
msgstr ""

#: src/Form/SettingsFieldset.php:46
msgid "Fallback when image is not pre-tiled"
msgstr ""

#: src/Form/SettingsFieldset.php:47
msgid ""
"When \"Zoomable viewer\" is selected above but the image is not pre-tiled, "
"this setting controls what is displayed instead. \"Zoomable with large\" "
"loads the large thumbnail in OpenSeadragon (limited zoom). \"Large "
"thumbnail\" falls back to the standard display. \"Zoomable with original\" "
"loads the original file in OpenSeadragon (good zoom but slow for large "
"files)."
msgstr ""

